%%{init: {'theme':'base','themeVariables':{'primaryColor':'#e7f5ff','fontFamily':'-apple-system,PingFang SC,sans-serif'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as 👤 用户
  participant Web as 🌐 任意网页
  participant CS as 🫧 SelectionBubble<br/>(Content Script)
  participant BG as ⚙️ Background SW
  participant EM as 🎯 EngineManager
  participant E as 🤖 引擎 (chrome-ai)

  U->>Web: 划选英文文本
  Web->>CS: selectionchange
  CS->>CS: composedPath 判定<br/>+ requestId 令牌
  CS-->>U: 显示气泡 [翻译]

  U->>CS: 点击「翻译」
  CS->>BG: postMessage<br/>{mode:'translate', text}
  BG->>EM: run(input)
  EM->>EM: pickBest by mode
  EM->>E: engine.run(input)
  E-->>EM: "你好世界"
  EM-->>BG: {text, from:'chrome-ai'}
  BG-->>CS: 结果
  CS-->>U: 气泡内展示译文
